addprefix.name: addprefix
addprefix.desc: Adds the provided prefix to the list of Mizu prefixes.

addrole.name: addrole
addrole.desc: Adds the specified role to the specified user.

ban.name: ban
ban.desc: Bans a specified user for a specified reason.
ban.note: Make sure a ban logs channel has been set to acquire the logs.

blacklistadd.name: blacklistadd
blacklistadd.desc: Adds a word or a string of words to the chat filter.
blacklistadd.note: There should only be one space between the command and the Word(s)

blacklistdel.name: blacklistdel
blacklistdel.desc: Removes a word or a string of words from the chat filter.
blacklistdel.note: There should only be one space between the command and the Word(s)

delprefix.name: delprefix
delprefix.desc: Removes the given prefix from the list of Mizu prefixes.

getsettings.name: getsettings
getsettings.desc:
Gets the specified settings for the Guild.
Settings:
1. general
2. logchannels
3. antispam
4. warnactions

help.name: help
help.desc: Shows the usage of the specified command.

kick.name: kick
kick.desc: Kicks the specified user for the specified reason.
kick.note: Make sure a kick logs channel has been set to acquire the logs.

load.name: load
load.desc: Loads the specified command, making it usable again.

modload.name: modload
modload.desc: Loads all commands in the specified module.

modunload.name: modunload
modunload.desc: Unloads all commands in the specified module.

mute.name: mute
mute.note: Make sure a mute role has been set and it exists.
mute.desc: Mutes the specified user with options.

purge.name: purge
purge.desc: Deletes the specified amount of messages from the chat.

removerole.name: removerole
removerole.desc: Removes the specified role from the specified user.

report.name: report
report.desc: Reports the specified user for the specified reason or DMs the command user for the report.

setembcol.name: setembcol
setembcol.desc: Changes the default embed color for the Mizu.

setlogch.name: setlogch
setlogch.desc:
Sets the log channel for the specified event.
Events:
1. mute
2. kick
3. ban
4. warn
5. reports
6. msgdel
7. userupdate
8. suggest
9. oofchest

setmuterole.name: setmuterole
setmuterole.desc: Sets the default mute role for the guild.

spammutetime.name: spammutetime
spammutetime.desc: Sets the temporary mute time for spamming. (Default: 5 minutes)
spammutetime.note: Set to 0 to make the mute permanent.

spamsettings.name: spamsettings
spamsettings.desc: Changes the Anti-Spam settings (General or Similar) of the guild.

unload.name: unload
unload.desc: Unloads the specified command, making it unusable until loaded again.

warnactionset.name: warnactionset
warnactionset.desc: Allows customization of actions taken at different warning levels.

warndel.name: warndel
warndel.desc: Clears a user's active warning corresponding to the specified index.

warnlog.name: warnlog
warnlog.desc: Displays the warn logs of the specified user. (Command user if no specifications)

vclimit.name: vclimit
vclimit.desc: Sets a userlimit for a custom VC from 1-99 depending on the amount specified.
vclimit.note: Limit argument should be in the range 1-99 (Including 1 and 99).

vclock.name: vclock
vclock.desc: Locks the command user's custom VC.
vclock.note: Locking = setting the userlimit to the current amount of people in the VC.

vcname.name: vcname
vcname.desc: Changes the name of the command user's custom VC.

vcnolimit.name: vcnolimit
vcnolimit.desc: Removes the user limit on the command user's custom VC.

foxgirl.name: foxgirl
foxgirl.desc: Posts an image/gif of a foxgirl.

kitty.name: kitty
kitty.desc: Posts an image of a cat.

sbooru.name: sbooru
sbooru.desc: Returns a random image from safebooru based on the provided tags.
sbooru.note: Separate the tags with '+' and use '_' for spaces.

butt.name: butt
butt.desc: Posts an image with a butt.

anime.name: anime
anime.desc: Gets information about the specified anime.

avatar.name: avatar
avatar.desc: Posts the avatar of the specified user or the command user.

eventsping.name: eventsping
eventsping.note: Make sure an events role has been set for the guild.

inrole.name: inrole
inrole.desc: Displays members having the specified role.

manga.name: manga
manga.desc: Posts information about the specified manga.

pokedex.name: pokedex
pokedex.desc: Gets information about the specified pokemon.

suggest.name: suggest
suggest.desc: Takes a suggestion from the user and posts it in a suggestions channel.

leaderboard.name: leaderboard
leaderboard.desc: Posts the <PageNumber>'th page of the server exp leaderboard. (Page 1 if page number is not provided)

rank.name: rank
rank.desc: Posts the guild exp and rank stats of the user.

moduleblock.name: moduleblock
moduleblock.desc: Blocks all the specified module commands in the specified channel.

repeat.name: repeat
repeat.desc: Sets a message repeater over the specified interval

getrepeat.name: getrepeat
getrepeat.desc: Displays information about the user's repeater, if they have set one.

stoprepeat.name: stoprepeat
stoprepeat.desc: Stops the user's repeater (if they have set any).

modmail.name: modmail
modmail.desc:
Sets the minimum word requirement for ModMail.
Options :
1. **-ch** - Channel (Argument: <#Channel/ChannelID>)
2. **-cd** - Cooldown (Argument: <Time>)
3. **-ucd** - Undetailed Cooldown (Argument: <Time>)
4. **-dl** - Detail Limit (Argument: <Number>)

xpsettings.name: xpsettings
xpsettings.desc:
Changes the Guild xp settings.
Options:
1. Combo Increment Amount (-cia) <Number>
2. Combo Interval (-ci) <Time>
3. Max Combo (-mc) <Number>
4. Lowest xp Amount (-lxp) <Number>
5. Highest xp Amount (-hxp) <Number>
6. xp Cooldown (-xpc) <Time>
7. xp Multiplier (-xpm) <Number>

addxp.name: addxp
addxp.desc: Adds the designated amount of exp to the specified user.

restrictcmd.name: restrictcmd
restrictcmd.desc: Blocks the specified command for those whose highest role is lower in the role hierarchy than the provided role.

setxp.name: setxp
setxp.desc: Sets the specified user's xp to the specified amount.
